title: Texas A&M cheerleader Brianna Aguilera gleefully poses with boyfriend weeks before witnesses heard pair argue ahead of her fatal plunge
description: Texas A&M cheerleader Brianna Aguilera appeared to be glowing with happiness while posing next to her boyfriend just weeks before police said she jumped to her death from her 17-story apartment building.
